
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>TubeFlow – Converta YouTube para MP3 e MP4</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="data:image/svg+xml,
<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 100 100'>
  <rect width='100' height='100' rx='20' fill='%236f4cff'/>
  <polygon points='40,30 70,50 40,70' fill='white'/>
</svg>">


  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --purple: #6c5ce7;
      --purple-light: #a29bfe;
      --purple-dark: #5a4bd1;
      --teal: #00b894;
      --bg: #f4f5f7;
      --white: #ffffff;
      --text: #1a1a2e;
      --muted: #6b7280;
      --card-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(108,92,231,0.08);
      --radius: 20px;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* ── NAV ── */
    nav {
      background: var(--white);
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      padding: 0 48px;
      height: 64px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
    }

    .logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: var(--text);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .logo-icon {
      width: 36px; height: 36px;
      background: var(--purple);
      border-radius: 10px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    }

    .logo-icon svg { fill: white; width: 20px; height: 20px; }

    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 32px; list-style: none; }
    .nav-links a { text-decoration: none; color: var(--muted); font-weight: 500; font-size: .95rem; transition: color .2s; }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--text); }

    /* ── HERO ── */
    .hero {
      padding: 90px 24px 60px;
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      background: #ede9fe;
      color: var(--purple);
      font-size: .78rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: .08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 6px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    .badge svg { width: 14px; height: 14px; fill: var(--purple); }

    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 3.6rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1.15;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    h1 .mp3 { color: var(--purple); }
    h1 .mp4 { color: var(--teal); }

    .hero-sub {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      max-width: 520px;
      margin: 0 auto 40px;
    }

    /* ── CONVERTER BOX ── */
    .converter-box {
      background: var(--white);
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 32px;
      max-width: 680px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(108,92,231,0.12);
    }

    .url-input {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 16px 20px;
      border: 1.5px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 14px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-family: inherit;
      color: var(--text);
      outline: none;
      background: #fafafa;
      transition: border-color .2s, box-shadow .2s;
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
    }

    .url-input-wrap {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      padding: 14px 20px;
      border: 1.5px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: #fafafa;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      transition: border-color .2s;
    }

    .url-input-wrap:focus-within { border-color: var(--purple); box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(108,92,231,.1); }

    .url-input-wrap svg { flex-shrink: 0; color: #9ca3af; width: 20px; height: 20px; }

    .url-input-wrap input {
      border: none; background: transparent; outline: none;
      font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text); width: 100%;
    }

    .url-input-wrap input::placeholder { color: #9ca3af; }

    .format-tabs {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .tab {
      padding: 10px 28px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 1.5px solid #e5e7eb;
      background: transparent;
      font-family: inherit;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: .92rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all .2s;
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 7px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .tab.active {
      background: #ede9fe;
      border-color: var(--purple-light);
      color: var(--purple);
    }

    .tab svg { width: 16px; height: 16px; }

    .btn-primary {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 18px;
      background: var(--purple);
      color: white;
      font-family: inherit;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 14px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background .2s, transform .15s;
      letter-spacing: .01em;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--purple-dark); transform: translateY(-1px); }

    /* ── HOW IT WORKS ── */
    .section { padding: 80px 24px; }
    .section-title { text-align: center; font-size: clamp(1.7rem, 3vw, 2.2rem); font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .section-sub { text-align: center; color: var(--muted); font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 56px; }

    /* ── FEATURES ── */
    .features-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 24px;
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .feature-card {
      background: var(--white);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 36px 32px;
      box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
      transition: transform .2s, box-shadow .2s;
    }

    .feature-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 12px 36px rgba(108,92,231,0.14); }

    .feature-icon {
      width: 52px; height: 52px;
      background: #ede9fe;
      border-radius: 14px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
    }

    .feature-icon svg { width: 26px; height: 26px; color: var(--purple); }

    .feature-card h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .feature-card p { color: var(--muted); font-size: .95rem; line-height: 1.65; }

    /* ── STEPS ── */
    .steps-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 32px;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .step-num {
      width: 48px; height: 48px;
      background: var(--purple);
      color: white;
      border-radius: 50%;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      margin: 0 auto 18px;
    }

    .step h3 { font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .step p { color: var(--muted); font-size: .93rem; }

    /* ── FAQ ── */
    .faq-list {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .faq-item {
      background: var(--white);
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .faq-q {
      width: 100%; background: none; border: none;
      padding: 22px 28px;
      font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text);
      text-align: left; cursor: pointer;
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .faq-q .chevron {
      flex-shrink: 0; width: 20px; height: 20px;
      color: var(--purple); transition: transform .25s;
    }

    .faq-item.open .chevron { transform: rotate(180deg); }

    .faq-a {
      max-height: 0; overflow: hidden;
      transition: max-height .35s ease, padding .25s;
      padding: 0 28px;
      color: var(--muted); font-size: .95rem; line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .faq-item.open .faq-a { max-height: 200px; padding: 0 28px 22px; }

    /* ── CTA ── */
    .cta-section { padding: 0 24px 80px; }

    .cta-box {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6c5ce7 0%, #8b5cf6 50%, #4f46e5 100%);
      border-radius: 28px;
      padding: 72px 40px;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .cta-box::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='60' height='60' viewBox='0 0 60 60' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cg fill='none' fill-rule='evenodd'%3E%3Cg fill='%23ffffff' fill-opacity='0.04'%3E%3Cpath d='M36 34v-4h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2h-4zm0-30V0h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2V6h4V4h-4zM6 34v-4H4v4H0v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2H6zM6 4V0H4v4H0v2h4v4h2V6h4V4H6z'/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    }

    .cta-deco {
      position: absolute; right: 48px; top: 50%;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      opacity: .25;
    }

    .cta-deco svg { width: 100px; height: 100px; fill: white; }

    .cta-box h2 { font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.6rem); font-weight: 800; color: white; margin-bottom: 14px; position: relative; }
    .cta-box p { color: rgba(255,255,255,.85); font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 36px; position: relative; }

    .btn-white {
      display: inline-block;
      background: white;
      color: var(--purple);
      font-family: inherit;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1rem;
      padding: 16px 40px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 14px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform .2s, box-shadow .2s;
      position: relative;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .btn-white:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.15); }

    /* ── FOOTER ── */
    footer {
      background: var(--white);
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      padding: 56px 48px 40px;
    }

    .footer-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.6fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 48px;
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto 48px;
    }

    .footer-brand p { color: var(--muted); font-size: .9rem; margin-top: 14px; line-height: 1.7; max-width: 240px; }

    .footer-col h4 { font-weight: 700; font-size: .9rem; margin-bottom: 18px; color: var(--text); }
    .footer-col a { display: block; color: var(--muted); font-size: .9rem; text-decoration: none; margin-bottom: 10px; transition: color .2s; }
    .footer-col a:hover { color: var(--text); }

    .social-icons { display: flex; gap: 12px; }
    .social-icon {
      width: 40px; height: 40px;
      border: 1.5px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 10px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      color: var(--muted); text-decoration: none;
      transition: border-color .2s, color .2s;
    }

    .social-icon:hover { border-color: var(--purple); color: var(--purple); }
    .social-icon svg { width: 18px; height: 18px; }

    .footer-bottom {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding-top: 28px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: .85rem;
    }

    /* ── MODAL ── */
    #modalOverlay {
      position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 999;
      background: rgba(15, 10, 40, 0.65);
      backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      opacity: 0; pointer-events: none;
      transition: opacity .3s ease;
    }

    #modalOverlay.active { opacity: 1; pointer-events: all; }

    .modal {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 28px;
      padding: 48px 40px 40px;
      width: 90%; max-width: 460px;
      box-shadow: 0 32px 80px rgba(108,92,231,.25);
      position: relative;
      transform: translateY(24px) scale(.96);
      transition: transform .35s cubic-bezier(.34,1.56,.64,1);
    }

    #modalOverlay.active .modal { transform: translateY(0) scale(1); }

    .modal-x {
      position: absolute; top: 18px; right: 18px;
      background: #f4f5f7; border: none; border-radius: 50%;
      width: 36px; height: 36px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      cursor: pointer; color: var(--muted);
      transition: background .2s, color .2s;
    }
    .modal-x:hover { background: #ede9fe; color: var(--purple); }

    .modal-icon-wrap {
      position: relative;
      width: 88px; height: 88px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    }

    .modal-spinner {
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 4px solid #ede9fe;
      border-top-color: var(--purple);
      animation: spin 1s linear infinite;
    }

    @keyframes spin { to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }

    .modal-icon-inner {
      width: 68px; height: 68px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--purple), #8b5cf6);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(108,92,231,.35);
    }

    .modal-title {
      font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .modal-sub {
      color: var(--muted); font-size: .95rem; transition: opacity .3s;
    }

    .progress-wrap {
      width: 100%;
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px;
    }

    .progress-track {
      flex: 1; height: 10px;
      background: #ede9fe;
      border-radius: 999px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .progress-fill {
      height: 100%; width: 0%;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--purple), #a29bfe);
      border-radius: 999px;
      transition: width .08s linear;
    }

    .progress-pct {
      font-weight: 700; font-size: .9rem;
      color: var(--purple); min-width: 36px; text-align: right;
    }

    .modal-hint {
      font-size: .85rem; color: #9ca3af; text-align: center;
    }

    .modal-success-icon {
      width: 88px; height: 88px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00b894, #00cec9);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(0,184,148,.3);
      animation: popIn .4s cubic-bezier(.34,1.56,.64,1);
    }

    @keyframes popIn { from { transform: scale(0); opacity: 0; } to { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; } }

    .btn-download {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
      background: var(--purple);
      color: white; font-family: inherit;
      font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem;
      padding: 15px 36px;
      border: none; border-radius: 14px; cursor: pointer;
      transition: background .2s, transform .15s;
    }
    .btn-download:hover { background: var(--purple-dark); transform: translateY(-1px); }

    .btn-close-link {
      background: none; border: none;
      font-family: inherit; color: var(--muted);
      font-size: .9rem; cursor: pointer;
      transition: color .2s;
    }
    .btn-close-link:hover { color: var(--text); }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      nav { padding: 0 20px; }
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
      .cta-deco { display: none; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
 <a href="/" class="logo">
  <div class="logo-icon">
    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100">
      <rect width="100" height="100" rx="20" fill="#6f4cff"/>
      <polygon points="40,30 70,50 40,70" fill="white"/>
    </svg>
  </div>
  TubeFlow
</a>

  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#recursos">Recursos</a></li>
    <li><a href="#como">Como funciona</a></li>
    <li><a href="#faq">FAQ</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="badge">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M13 2L4.09 12.97 12 12l-1 9 9-9.97L12 12l1-10z"/></svg>
    Rápido, Grátis e Ilimitado
  </div>
  <h1>Converta YouTube para<br><span class="mp3">MP3</span> e <span class="mp4">MP4</span> em segundos.</h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">A ferramenta mais simples para baixar seus vídeos favoritos. Sem anúncios irritantes, sem registros, apenas o conteúdo que você ama.</p>

  <div class="converter-box">
    <div class="url-input-wrap">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
        <rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="15" rx="2"/><polyline points="17 2 12 7 7 2"/>
      </svg>
      <input type="url" placeholder="Cole o link do YouTube aqui..." id="urlInput"/>
    </div>
    <div class="format-tabs">
      <button class="tab active" id="tabMP3" onclick="selectTab('MP3')">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 18V5l12-2v13"/><circle cx="6" cy="18" r="3"/><circle cx="18" cy="16" r="3"/></svg>
        MP3
      </button>
      <button class="tab" id="tabMP4" onclick="selectTab('MP4')">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="15" rx="2"/><polyline points="17 2 12 7 7 2"/></svg>
        MP4
      </button>
    </div>
    <button class="btn-primary" onclick="startConvert()">Começar Agora →</button>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FEATURES -->
<section class="section" id="recursos">
  <h2 class="section-title">Por que escolher o TubeFlow?</h2>
  <p class="section-sub">Tudo que você precisa em um só lugar</p>
  <div class="features-grid">
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M13 2L4.09 12.97 12 12l-1 9 9-9.97L12 12l1-10z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Ultra Rápido</h3>
      <p>Conversão instantânea. Seus arquivos ficam prontos em segundos.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Seguro e Privado</h3>
      <p>Nenhum dado é armazenado. Sua privacidade é nossa prioridade.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="5" y="2" width="14" height="20" rx="2"/><line x1="12" y1="18" x2="12.01" y2="18"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Multiplataforma</h3>
      <p>Funciona em qualquer dispositivo: celular, tablet ou computador.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 18v-6a9 9 0 0 1 18 0v6"/><path d="M21 19a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-1a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-3a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h3zM3 19a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h1a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-3a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H3z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Qualidade de Áudio</h3>
      <p>MP3 em até 320kbps. Som cristalino em seus fones.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M12 1v2M12 21v2M4.22 4.22l1.42 1.42M18.36 18.36l1.42 1.42M1 12h2M21 12h2M4.22 19.78l1.42-1.42M18.36 5.64l1.42-1.42"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Sem Instalação</h3>
      <p>Nada para instalar. Use diretamente do seu navegador.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="2" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12"/><path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Acesso Global</h3>
      <p>Disponível em qualquer lugar do mundo, sem restrições.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
